Type materials — Holotype and 7 paratype females were collected from samples of stored rice and decayed rice bran; 1 female paratype , decayed plant material; 3 female paratypes , livestock and poultry manure; 1 female paratype , birch and fig leaves; 2 female paratypes , soil; Khomam City ( 37° 23’ 21” N 49° 39’ 30” E , – 17 m ), 19 July 2017 ; 10 female paratypes , stored rice and decayed rice bran; 1 female paratype , livestock and poultry manure;
